    public class AHConfigLocalServiceImpl
extends AHConfigLocalServiceBaseImpl
    The implementation of the a h config local service.

    All custom service methods should be put in this class. Whenever methods are added, rerun ServiceBuilder to copy their definitions into the AHConfigLocalService interface.

    This is a local service. Methods of this service will not have security checks based on the propagated JAAS credentials because this service can only be accessed from within the same VM.

    Author:
    Brian Wing Shun Chan
